fields.lamptitle: ANTLER rustic stag antler ceiling pendant light

This beautifully hand crafted ceiling light is particularly suited for more traditional and rustic homes. The pendant is supported on a decorative link chain from a circular ceiling rose and the height can be adjusted if necessary by removing some links. Longer length chain is available if needed - please contact us if you would like to order this ceiling light with longer chain. This would be great for lighting the exterior of an traditional period property atop a gate post or bollard.

fields.lamptitle: OBLONG Rustic Table Lamp
fields.description1: A rustic eye-catching table lamp finished off in faded brown to show the wear and tear of the light to create that rustic feel. This stunning lamp features 2 exposed lamps which are perfect for decorative bulbs to really enhance the rustic feel. The stylish and simple design of the table lamp would add a sense of style to any room it is added to.

fields.lamptitle: OREGON 3 light rustic ceiling cluster pendant in cream
fields.description1: A decorative traditional 3 light ceiling pendant cluster in cream finish with frame shades, suitable for use in any rustic setting and ideal for those with medium to high ceilings. This would be ideal for lighting in long drop stairwells or over tables. This light is British made, designed and manufactured in the UK.

fields.lamptitle: ANTLER rustic bleached table lamp with natural shade
fields.description1: Part of the Designer Range this bleached Antler table lamp has the look of driftwood there is something delightfully simple and calming about the styling. You feel connected with nature which is why this lamp sits so well in rural settings. There is a darker version of this lamp which has a more traditional look but the paler antler table lamp is fresh and contemporary we show it complete with the natural colour shade however you could have this lamp made with a vibrant yellow for a small additional charge. Speak to our sales team who are happy to advise.

fields.lamptitle: IVAN 5 light rustic cluster ceiling pendant
fields.description1: A vintage industrial design 5 light ceiling pendant cluster with a dark oak wood effect suspended ring structure and antique brass lamp holders on braided cable. The braided cable pendants can be shortened accordingly by simply wrapping around the frame, this would be great for suspended the lamps at different heights for an abstract look. The light is double insulated for safe use without need of an earth wire and is suitable for use on a dimmer switch providing the bulbs used are dimmable.

fields.lamptitle: AIDA Rustic Modern Table Lamp in Natural Wood
fields.description1: A small table lamp made in natural wood which is designed to show off a decorative LED bulb. The nuances and rustic nature of wood add a rustic charm, whilst the small stature of the lamp ensures that it fits into modern designs. This is a great chance to own your own, unique lamp with a character all of it's own! Complete with an in-line rocker switch for ease of use, this looks fabulous in a sitting room or as a space saving bedside lamp.

fields.lamptitle: FACTORY 3 Light Semi Flush Ceiling Fitting Rustic Black
fields.description1: A great light to use in homes with lower ceilings, this is great in living rooms and high traffic areas, such as hallways and landings. It adds a real rustic industrial charm.

fields.lamptitle: CARYA Ceramic Table Lamp Rustic Luminaire, Black Clay
fields.description1: This rustic ceramic luminaire has an extraordinarily appealing façade that resembles the trunk of a Carya hickory tree.

fields.lamptitle: CANYA Ceramic Table Lamp Rustic Luminaire, Red Iron
fields.description1: This rustic ceramic luminaire, which resembles the trunk of a Carya hickory tree, has an unusually appealing façade.

fields.lamptitle: OBLONG Rustic Floor Lamp
fields.description1: A rustic 5-light floor lamp finished in black which has been sanded down to give a faded rustic finish. The Oblong floor lamp is ideal for illuminating areas of any living room, dining room, bedroom or hallway. The floor lamp would also look fantastic with its matching ceiling light and table lamp.

fields.lamptitle: RUSTICA Hanging Wall Light in Oak and Antique Brass
fields.description1: A vintage inspired hanging wall light in an antique brass and oak wood finish. This wall light uses a playful 'wrap around' design that would suit a range of interior design schemes. This light utilises a bare bulb aesthetic, offering the opportunity to pair with a decorative bulb of your choice. Wall lights are great for creating ambiance within homes and this wall light can be dimmed when paired with a suitable bulb and switch.

fields.lamptitle: RUSTICA 3 Light Ceiling Pendant Bar Medium Oak and Antique Brass
fields.description1: A stylish modern industrial ceiling pendant bar light that features an oak rose and cylinder bar with three antique brass lamp holders. This retro-inspired ceiling light can hang to a maximum of 66cm, making it the perfect light to hang above a breakfast bar or kitchen island. This ceiling light can be height adjusted upon installation or the wires can be wrapped around the bar for a vintage aesthetic.

fields.lamptitle: RUSTICA 4 Light Ceiling Pendant Bar Medium Oak and Antique Brass
fields.description1: A stylish modern industrial ceiling pendant bar light that features an oak rose and cylinder bar with four antique brass lamp holders. This retro-inspired ceiling light can hang to a maximum of 165cm, making it the perfect light to hang above a breakfast bar or kitchen island. This ceiling light can be height adjusted upon installation or the wires can be wrapped around the bar for a vintage aesthetic.

fields.lamptitle: KYLE rustic wall sconce in bronze with onyx candle effect shade
fields.description1: Forged style wall light 'Kyle' has a delightful mix or contemporary and traditional design influences. Bronzed metalwork holds a fabulous deep rich butterscotch onyx pillar candle shade. Onyx is a natural stone a mottled semi translucent quartz. Very luxurious a quality light fitting which would look wonderful in many situations, both home and business applications such as hotels, restaurants and bars to name a few!
